OL,3,CProlific fare evaders targeted in
OL,4,Cmajor crackdown on London Underground
OL,6,FTransport bosses are targeting
OL,7,Fprolific fare evaders to crack down on
OL,8,Fevasion across London Underground.
OL,10,FProfessional investigators will single
OL,11,Fout people across the network using
OL,12,Fadvanced technology to halve revenue
OL,13,Floss.
OL,15,FMore than 500 uniformed Transport for
OL,16,FLondon officers are already patrolling
OL,17,Fthe network to tackle the problem.
