OL,3,CProlific fare evaders targeted in
OL,4,Cmajor crackdown on London Underground
OL,6,FTfL wants to halve fare evasion across
OL,7,Fservices to 1.5 per cent or less by
OL,8,F2030. Revenue is critical to
OL,9,Fsustaining safe, clean, and reliable
OL,10,Fpublic transport.
OL,12,FThe Mayor of London, Sadiq Khan, said:
OL,13,F"Fare evasion is a criminal offence
OL,14,Fwhich deprives TfL of thousands of
OL,15,Fpounds of vital revenue every year
OL,16,Fthat could be reinvested in London's
OL,17,Ftransport network.
