OL,3,CProlific fare evaders targeted in
OL,4,Cmajor crackdown on London Underground
OL,6,F"That's why we're expanding our team
OL,7,Fof professional investigators to cover
OL,8,Fthe whole network and investing in the
OL,9,Flatest technology to target the worst
OL,10,Foffenders. It sends a clear message:
OL,11,Ffare evasion will not be tolerated,
OL,12,Fand we will hold those who do it to
OL,13,Faccount.
