OL,3,CProlific fare evaders targeted in
OL,4,Cmajor crackdown on London Underground
OL,6,F"The team is supporting more than 500
OL,7,Funiformed TfL officers across the
OL,8,Fnetwork who are already going after
OL,9,Ffare evaders and helping to keep the
OL,10,Fpublic safe. The latest data shows
OL,11,Fthat TfL's efforts to reduce fare
OL,12,Fevasion on the network is working, but
OL,13,Fthere is more to do.
OL,15,F"I'm determined to do all I can to
OL,16,Fsupport the vital work TfL is doing to
OL,17,Fensure these vital funds are
OL,18,Freinvested into improving transport
OL,19,Fservices for Londoners."
