OL,3,CProlific fare evaders targeted in
OL,4,Cmajor crackdown on London Underground
OL,6,FOne major area of focus for TfL's
OL,7,Fenforcement teams is contactless
OL,8,Fpayment card fare evasion.
OL,10,FIn one recent case, an individual used
OL,11,Fa contactless payment card to evade
OL,12,Fpaying the correct fare across 202
OL,13,Fjourneys.
OL,15,FAfter investigation, the individual
OL,16,Fwas ordered to pay #1,472 in fines,
OL,17,Fone of the thousands who are caught
OL,18,Fand prosecuted each year, resulting in
OL,19,Ffinancial penalties and criminal
OL,20,Fconvictions.
